<A>__{a skinny white arm suddenly shoots out from wild bill's cell and grabs coffey by the wrist. the men gasp, shocked to see billy on his feet, grinning and weaving like a punch drunk. coffey's reaction is beyond simple surprise; he's actually trembling at billy's touch as if some electrical circuit were engaged. his eyes are wide and horrified, as if he'd just put his hand in a basket full of snakes. he tries to pull away, but billy has him tight, that mysterious circuit blazing.}
